Package: pft
Type: Package
Title: Compute ATS-Compliant PFT Reference Values
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Pat Johnson, Jairo Pena, and Zach Quicksall
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: Computes upper/lower limits of normal and predicted
    values according to ATS-defined standards for pulmonary function tests.
    This includes spirometry, lung volumes, and diffusion capacity.
